{{Politics of Greenland}}
'''The First Cabinet of Kim Kielsen''' is the current government of the [[Greenland]]. It was appointed on 10 December 2014 with [[Kim Kielsen]] from [[Siumut|Forward (Siumut)]] as Prime Minister,<ref>[http://naalakkersuisut.gl/da/Naalakkersuisut/Nyheder/2014/12/101214-Naalakkersuisussat naalakkersuisut.gl, Government]</ref> making a coalition between [[Siumut|Forward (Siumut)]], [[Demokraatit|Democrats (Demokraatit)]] and [[Solidarity (Greenland)|Solidarity (Atassut)]]. It is a [[majority government]] and is right and left winged government.

==List of ministers ==
The Social Democratic Siumut has 5 ministers including the Prime Minister. The Social liberal Democrats has 2 ministers. The Liberalistic Solidarity has 2 ministers.

